- fuzz testing
- log exceptions separately for plint_web

- change additions to give numerical syllable count for affected syllable
- adjust the diaeresis uncertainty threshold to assert that all verses are
  correct (change your opinion about the syllable with least confidence)
- document expected errors of test.sh and commit necessary files
- remove kludge for invalid characters, split them in specific chunks
- improve performance with profiling

== Error reporting ==

- produce error reports first to structured and then to text and json
- and then from json to html
- indiquer l'état des hémistiches seulement s'il y a un problème, et seulement
  pour les syllabes plausibles
- highlight possible hemistiche positions where an hemistiche could have been placed

== Evaluation ==

- évaluer sur la base de données lexique, sur la qualité de la génération, sur
  le nombre d'erreurs reconnues en cross-validation

== Rules ==

- other examples of "mentions", "notions" ? ...

== Other approaches ==

- learn rhyme and gender agnostically by clustering: prepare an undirected graph
  of rhyming verses, factor out suffixes, do SCC, prepare a trie

